name: The Duel: Test Drive II Car Disk: The Muscle Cars
overview: This addon for Test Drive II features 5 legendary cars like a 1963 Corvette Sting Ray, a 1968 Shelby GT500 Cobra, a 1967 Pontiac GTO, a 1969 COPO 9560 ZL-1 Camaro and a 1969 Dodge Charger Daytona. As usual the original game is needed to enjoy the addon.
